---
const linkClass =
  "block text-brown-light no-underline text-[0.85rem] mb-2.5 hover:text-cream transition-colors";
---

<footer class="bg-brown-dark text-brown-light pt-[60px] pb-10 px-6">
  <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 md:gap-10">
    <div class="col-span-2 md:col-span-1">
      <div class="font-extrabold text-[1.2rem] text-cream mb-3">바위로드</div>
      <p class="text-[0.82rem] leading-[1.7]">
        바위처럼 든든한 어학연수 로드맵.
        <br />
        비용 공개, 솔직 비교, 수수료 제로.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="text-[0.8rem] font-bold text-cream mb-4 uppercase tracking-wider">서비스</div>
      <a href="/academies" class={linkClass}>어학원 비교</a>
      <a href="/#cost" class={linkClass}>비용 가이드</a>
      <a href="/quote?from=footer" class={linkClass}>무료 견적</a>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="text-[0.8rem] font-bold text-cream mb-4 uppercase tracking-wider">약관 및 정책</div>
      <a href="/terms" class={linkClass}>이용약관</a>
      <a href="/privacy" class={linkClass}>개인정보처리방침</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="mt-10 pt-6 border-t border-white/10 text-center text-[0.75rem] text-brown">
    <p class="mb-2">바위로드 | 대표: - | 사업자등록번호: -</p>
    <p class="mb-3">통신판매업 신고번호: - | 이메일: contact@bawiroad.com</p>
    <p>&copy; 2026 바위로드 (Bawi Road). All rights reserved.</p>
  </div>
</footer>
